        </div><!--/card-content-->

    </a><!-- /card action -->


    <a href="https://afo-prod-cd.sitecore-prod-ase3.appserviceenvironment.net/research-and-data/data" class="card action  ">
        <div class="card-content">
                        <h2 class="card-title">
                            Data
                        </h2>

            <p>The Federal Reserve Bank of Atlanta produces several sets of interactive charts and data visualizations focused on a variety of national and regional economic conditions, such as the labor market, housing and real estate, inflation, and small business.</p>
            <div class="arrow-link">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" role="img">
                    <title>Icon for Link Arrow</title>
