        </div><!--/card-content-->

    </a><!-- /card action -->


    <a href="https://afo-prod-cd.sitecore-prod-ase3.appserviceenvironment.net/who-we-are/visit/general-information" class="card action  ">
        <div class="card-content">
                        <h2 class="card-title">
                            General Information
                        </h2>

            <p>The Atlanta Fed serves the Sixth Federal Reserve District, which encompasses Alabama, Florida, Georgia, and sections of Louisiana, Mississippi, and Tennessee.</p>
            <div class="arrow-link">
                <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="40" height="40" viewBox="0 0 40 40" fill="none" role="img">
                    <title>Icon for Link Arrow</title>
